  "prompt": "How can I reach Infosys Pocharam campus from Ameerpet?",
  "response": "To reach the Infosys Pocharam campus from Ameerpet, you have several transportation options:\n\n### By Car or Taxi:\n1. **Self-Driving**: You can use Google Maps for the most accurate directions based on live traffic conditions. The journey typically takes about 30 to 45 minutes, depending on traffic.\n2. **Ride-Hailing Services**: You can use apps like Uber or Ola. Simply enter \"Infosys Pocharam\" as your destination, and the app will provide an estimated fare and time.\n\n### By Public Transport:\n1. **Bus**: You can take a bus from Ameerpet to Pocharam. Look for buses heading towards Pocharam or nearby areas. Buses might not have a direct route, and you may need to change buses, so check the schedule in advance.\n2. **Train/Local Transit**: Depending on the local transit options available, you may also check if there are any local trains or metro options connecting Ameerpet with the nearest stations to Pocharam.\n\n### By Two-Wheeler:\nIf you have access to a two-wheeler, you can also ride to Infosys. The roads are typically manageable, and parking is available at the campus.\n\n### Tips:\n- **Check Traffic Updates**: Traffic can vary significantly during peak hours, so it\u2019s advisable to check live traffic conditions before you leave.\n- **Plan Ahead**: If you are taking public transport, verify the timings and availability of buses or trains to avoid long waits.\n\nMake sure to confirm the best route based on your travel time and preference!",
